      "body": "**T6 has no cleanly-reachable work: proofs Mathlib-gap-blocked + cleanup needs blueprint scope T6 lacks.**\n\n**Recommendation: do not spend a Horizon proof session on T6 as currently scoped \u2014 redirect or re-scope it.** Ground verified this against a green Albanese `lake build` (8581 jobs, EXIT 0).\n\n**1. All 4 T6 proof targets are hard-blocked on absent Mathlib v4.31 API** (details + line numbers in the `ALB.codim1` roadmap comment):\n\n- `isRegularLocalRing_stalk_of_smooth` non-closed-point case \u2192 **Stacks 00OF** (large homological build; memory says do not attempt).\n- Milne 3.1 `extend_of_codimOneFree_of_smooth` \u2192 **0AVF** + 00OF.\n- Milne 3.3 `indeterminacy_pure_codim_one_into_grpScheme` \u2192 function-field-pullback bridge + codim-1 diagonal-intersection.\n- Thm32 `av_codimOneFree_of_indeterminacy` \u2192 transitively consumes Milne 3.1/3.3.\n\nNone is proof-search debt; a Horizon slot spent here would either idle or burn on a blocked 00OF build.\n\n**2. T6 one \"safe\" target \u2014 the dead-code cleanup \u2014 is mis-scoped and Horizon cannot complete it.**\n\n- The superseded chain in `CodimOneExtension.lean` is **L628\u2013882** (~255 LOC, all `private`, unreferenced by live code; superseded by `StandardSmoothDimension.lean`), not the L647\u2013871 stated in T6.\n- Deleting it requires removing/re-pointing **9 blueprint `\\lean` nodes** (`Albanese_CodimOneExtension.tex` L1148\u20131495) \u2014 and one **live** node (`matsumura_isRegular_of_linearIndependent_cotangent`) `\\cref`s a dead label at L1638, so it is not a mechanical block-delete.\n- **T6 write_set is Lean-only** (`CodimOneExtension`, `StandardSmoothDimension`, `Thm32`); it excludes `blueprint/**`. A Horizon T6 agent that deletes the Lean would leave 9 dangling blueprint pins it cannot fix.\n\n**Options:**\n- (a) Let **Ground** do the full Lean+blueprint cleanup in a focused pass (recommended \u2014 only role that can touch both; analysis is done).\n- (b) Add `blue