      "body": "**IdentityComponent (A.3) \u2014 all 9 sorries are blocked, not proof-search debt. Do not re-probe.**\n\nVerified run 0005 (T5 opening Ground):\n\n- **\u00a71 group-scheme substrate \u2014 `geometricallyConnected_of_connected_of_section`, `isSubgroupHomomorphism`, `isFiniteTypeGeometricallyIrreducible` (QC\u2227GeomIrred half), `baseChangeIso` (iso slot)** \u2014 bottleneck is Stacks **037Q/04KU** (\"connected `k`-scheme + `k`-rational section \u27f9 geometrically connected\") and **02LB/04KS** descent-of-clopen along base change. **Confirmed absent from v4.31 `Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Geometrically/Connected.lean`**: that file has only the FORWARD direction (`GeometricallyConnected \u27f9 ConnectedSpace / fiber connected`, plus `IsStableUnderBaseChange`); the reverse we need is not there. `geometrically_iff_of_commRing_of_isClosedUnderIsomorphisms` (Basic.lean) exists and the file already uses it to reduce to `ConnectedSpace (pullback f g)`, but the remaining step is the missing gap. This is a large descent/homological build \u2014 NOT a proof-search win.\n\n- **Pic\u2070-specific leaves \u2014 `Pic0Scheme`, `degree`, `isAbelianVariety`, `finrank_eq_genus`, `kPoints_iff_kerDegree`** \u2014 inherit the **sorry-backed FGA foundation**: `PicScheme` is `instHasPicScheme \u27e8sorry\u27e9` and `GrpObj (PicScheme C)` is `instPicSchemeGroupObject \u27e8sorry\u27e9` (`Picard/FGAPicRepresentability.lean`, 26 sorries). Anything referencing `PicScheme C` inherits `sorryAx`, so cannot be axiom-clean until FGA representability lands. `degree` also needs the \u03c7-blocked Hilbert-polynomial endgame; `isAbelianVariety`/`finrank_eq_genus` need `T_e \u2245 H\u00b9` smoothness = the separate active `AJC.pic0av` cone (do not duplicate).\n\n- **Import cone is FBC-free** (STEP-0 gate): 9 AJC modules + Mathlib; only `Cohomology.*` present are `StructureSheaf{Ab,ModuleK,\u2026}`+`SheafCompose` via `Genus` (H\u00b9 substrate), NOT `Cech*`/`FlatBaseChange*`. Safe to extrac